5
00:00:14,629 --> 00:00:16,180
I’m your host Chris Chappell.

6
00:00:16,180 --> 00:00:19,430
For decades, North Korea and China were besties.

7
00:00:19,430 --> 00:00:20,920
Together like peas and carrots.

8
00:00:20,920 --> 00:00:22,380
Like rice and gochujang.

9
00:00:22,380 --> 00:00:24,939
But recently, China has been spending

10
00:00:24,939 --> 00:00:27,650
a bit too much time with the US,

11
