and they keep talking about North Korea

12
00:00:29,070 --> 00:00:30,520
behind its back,

13
00:00:30,540 --> 00:00:34,300
about how it’s been getting all nuclear lately.

14
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:35,660
And now China’s telling North Korea

15
00:00:35,661 --> 00:00:38,800
that maybe they can't even be friends anymore.

16
00:00:38,800 --> 00:00:40,700
Poor Kim Jong-Un must be so sad!

17
00:00:40,700 --> 00:00:44,399
But fortunately, he might have made a new
friend.

18
00:00:44,399 --> 00:00:47,079
A big, strong, manly friend.

19
00:00:47,079 --> 00:00:48,309
No, not me!

20
00:00:48,309 --> 00:00:49,309
Vladamir Putin!

21
00:00:49,309 --> 00:00:50,829
