22
00:00:50,829 --> 00:00:51,829
Think about it.

23
00:00:51,829 --> 00:00:53,610
Putin’s an outdoorsman...

24
00:00:53,610 --> 00:00:55,489
...a friend to the animals...

25
00:00:55,489 --> 00:00:57,090
...and beloved by children.

26
00:00:57,090 --> 00:00:59,559
That’s a perfect match for Kim!

27
00:00:59,559 --> 00:01:01,340
He’s an outdoorsman...

28
00:01:01,340 --> 00:01:03,820
...friend to the animals...-ish

29
