all going to summer re-education camp.

33
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:14,860
Don't worry kids,

34
00:01:14,860 --> 00:01:16,090
it'll be great.

35
00:01:16,090 --> 00:01:18,020
Talent shows!

36
00:01:18,020 --> 00:01:19,430
Archery!

37
00:01:19,430 --> 00:01:21,120
Making arts and crafts for export

38
